data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Rogersville. This charming 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom brick home is the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Nestled in a peaceful town setting, this residence offers proximity to schools, making it an ideal choice for families. Key Features: ~2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom: Enjoy the perfect balance of cozy living spaces and practical design. ~Brick Exterior: Built to last, this home boasts a classic brick exterior that exudes timeless appeal. ~School Proximity: Benefit from the convenience of having schools nearby, making the morning routine a breeze for your family. ~Quaint Town Setting: Experience the charm of small-town living while still enjoying easy access to essential amenities. Whether you're a first time home buyer or looking to downsize, this property offers a warm and inviting environment. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming brick home your own. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and take the next step toward calling Rogersville, TN your home!
